    Create Music Feature

    ✨ AI Music Generator: Create Instrumental Music

    Create Instrumental Music

    Sometimes, we just want to create a piece of pure music that suits our current mood, without vocals or lyrics. We can use the [Instrumental] function to describe the effect you expect from the pure music, and then give it to AI Music Generator to generate it with one click.

    ✨ AI Music Generator: Create Normal Music

    Create Normal Music

    If you want the song to have vocals, you can use the [Normal] function, fill in the lyrics, style, and title, and then AI Music Generator can help you generate a song product that meets your expectations with one click.

    Questions & Answers

    ?
    How to use the Create Music feature of AI Music Generator?

    Visit https://makebestmusic.com/app/create-music, you can go to the create music function page, and then you will find that AI Music Generator provides Instrumental and Normal options, where Instrumental is used to generate pure music, while Normal generates music with singers singing.

    ?
    How does the Create Music function control the rhythm of generated music?

    AI Music Generator provides a very simple operation page. Although the page is simple, it can actually be controlled in a more detailed manner.You can read https://makebestmusic.com/blog/song-structure-ai-generation-guide to learn how to control the generated music by controlling the lyrics.

    ?
    Can I use the music I create to make money on Youtube or other platforms?

    Hello, if you are a paying user, you can directly use the generated music to generate revenue. The copyright of the music generated by AI belongs to you, so please feel free to use it.

    ?
    Is it possible to download drum beats, vocals, etc. in the generated song?

    The create music function can help you generate complete music based on text, but it cannot split the music. You can use AI Music Generator's split music to split the music.
